      <p>I have added <term xml:lang="ta">puḷḷi</term>-s in my transcription, and rendered even the hypercorrected '<term xml:lang="ta">ē</term>' as such. Thus, I surmise that '<term xml:lang="ta">pēyarakarāti</term>' is '<term xml:lang="ta">peyarakarāti</term>' — the dictionary on nouns.</p></encodingDesc>
